## 📋 Google Sheets Column Setup

Create a sheet with these exact headers:

| A | B | C | D | E | F | G | H | I | J | K |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| customer_name | customer_phone | customer_email | product_name | quantity | unit_price | total_price | order_date | shipping_address | order_status | recorded_at |

---

## 🔧 Common Issues

| Problem | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| JS Normalizer returns empty fields | AI used unexpected key names | Check execution log, add the new key to `findField` candidates |
| Wrong timezone on order_date | `$now` uses server timezone | Use `$now.setZone('Africa/Cairo')` |
| Webhook returns 404 | Workflow not activated | Click **Activate** toggle in n8n |
| Agent returns markdown fences | Model hallucination | Already handled by the normalizer automatically |
| CORS error on webhook | ngrok/server config | Add `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *` header in n8n webhook settings |

